&lt;li&gt;You will be adaptable and agile in your approach to the different retailers you work with by understanding their specific company culture.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You will identify and work to resolve inventory, staffing, branding, or merchandising needs at the market level.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You will ensure that each store is trained frequently and reinforce that training with follow up selling techniques, demonstrations, and product information&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You will develop and maintain an organized system that ensures appropriate levels of testers, gratis, sampling &amp;amp; training materials&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You will identify and report market information with leadership to ensure market growth&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You will execute Supergoop! marketing initiatives&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You will maintain Supergoop! image and brand standards by adhering to merchandising guidelines. You will coach your team on this and hold them accountable to the same expectations.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
