&lt;li&gt;You will analyze sales reports to identify trends and opportunities and execute accordingly&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You will manage and develop an area support team for your territory through consistent touch bases to assure strong communication and partnership alignment.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
