&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Cross-Functional Collaboration: &lt;/strong&gt;Partner closely with FP&amp;amp;A, Marketing, and Operations teams to ensure accurate and timely financial data processing&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Financial Reporting:&lt;/strong&gt; Assist in the preparation of monthly, quarterly, and annual financial reports; support ad hoc financial analyses as requested by senior leadership&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Systems and Process Improvement:&lt;/strong&gt; Identify opportunities to streamline accounting workflows and improve accuracy and efficiency; assist with system implementations or upgrades as needed&lt;/li&gt;
